title: Muhammad Shehbaz Sharif of PML-N wins PP-158
content:
ISLAMABAD, Feb 9 (APP): Muhammad Shehbaz Sharif of Pakistan Muslim League Nawaz President (PML-N) has won the election for Punjab Assembly constituency PP-158 Lahore-XIV by securing 38,642 votes.
According to the unofficial result issued by the Returning Officer/ECP, his runner-up was an independent Yousaf Ali, who bagged 23,847 votes.
Votersâ€™ turnout remained 48.11%.
